PHP-LevelDB: PHP Bindings for LevelDB
=============

Installation
=============

Requirements:
1. Install leveldb from: <http://code.google.com/p/leveldb/>

leveldb didn't have install in Makefile, you need to copy yourself.
eg:

	$ cd leveldb-1.4.0
	$ make
	$ cp -r include /usr/local
	$ cp -r libleveldb* /usr/local/lib

2.1 Install from source
2.2 Install from PECL

Usage
============

	<?php
	
	$db = new LevelDB("/tmp/leveldb-test");
	$db->put($key, $value);


